  <brief_title>Dietetic Efficacy of Mare's Milk for Patients With Chronic Inflammatory Bowel Diseases</brief_title>
  <official_title>Dietetic Effects of Mare's Milk in Patients With Chronic Inflammatory Bowel Diseases (IBD) - a Double Blind Placebo Controlled Cross-over Study.</official_title>
